# Connect with Walipa

## Online Community
We utilize the Open Social platform to 
coordinate our global efforts. Once 
registered, you can join local 
stewardship groups and participate in 
our document database.

## Regional Hub
Our primary physical stewardship 
operations are located in Nevada County, 
California.

## Reach Out
For inquiries regarding land trusts, 
seed distribution, or the stewardship 
manifesto, please contact us at:
* **Email**: contact@walipa.org
* **GitHub**: LowellMontgomery/walipa.org

## A Note on Privacy
Walipa values your privacy. We do not 
track users or sell data. We are 
supported by the community, for the 
living planet.